query:
UPDATE customers
             SET full_name = $1,
                 phone_number_enc = $2,
                 phone_number_nonce = $3,
                 phone_number_hash = $4,
                 email_enc = $5,
                 email_nonce = $6,
                 email_hash = $7,
                 address_enc = $8,
                 address_nonce = $9
             WHERE uuid = $10
